    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WIshlist Now!</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/e99e9264a5013be50b0c05be8e588785.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic and In-Depth Gunplay and Gun Manipulation With a Variety of Unique Weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/4fe20363a21af579aa9cb61b3d930410.poster.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/4fe20363a21af579aa9cb61b3d930410.webm?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/4fe20363a21af579aa9cb61b3d930410.mp4?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smart and unique enemy behavior and NPC interactions</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/7edd4ec6bdee6c7f7ec30134a01a8613.poster.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/7edd4ec6bdee6c7f7ec30134a01a8613.webm?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/7edd4ec6bdee6c7f7ec30134a01a8613.mp4?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Atmospheric horror of the deadly Containment Zone</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/a82780b3c808a602214e034ea52d217a.poster.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/a82780b3c808a602214e034ea52d217a.webm?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/a82780b3c808a602214e034ea52d217a.mp4?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interactible Environments and looting system</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/bdfb89e07db652cef125e974c564e329.poster.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/bdfb89e07db652cef125e974c564e329.webm?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/bdfb89e07db652cef125e974c564e329.mp4?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inventory management</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/d73622bc43786d3bdc2115f234a93a7f.poster.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/d73622bc43786d3bdc2115f234a93a7f.webm?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/d73622bc43786d3bdc2115f234a93a7f.mp4?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic Healing and Medicine System</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/3e6f46a29c7e88d83cedf842ea340816.poster.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/3e6f46a29c7e88d83cedf842ea340816.webm?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/3e6f46a29c7e88d83cedf842ea340816.mp4?t=1716609862\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Semi-Open World</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/6edafc866dfaa84d374bd90f77619320.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Day-Night transitions and variety of atmospheric weather systems</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/267fd0b7ba66e7257d57da3af3da5ab1.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survival aspects: Hunger, Radiation, Infection and Hydration system</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich story</h2></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Online Co-op and PVP multiplayer modes implemented shortly after release</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/Steam_Description_resize_swamp__2_.PNG?t=1716609862\" /></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thrilling Tactical Combat and Story</h2>The year is 1995, only a couple of years after the collapse of the Soviet Union, and Russia is trying to recollect all of its past scientific endeavors and research located in the new post-soviet states. The Object 1611 laboratory located in the Soldanesti district in Moldova has suffered from an anomalous malfunction that has caused contamination of the Soldanesti Containment Zone, radiation leaks, and a containment breach of live soviet experiments into the surrounding area. <br>Containment Zone is a hardcore, tactical, realistic RPG looter shooter set in a fictional post-apocalyptic scenario in the Soldanesti District of the Republic of Moldova where the player takes the role of Vadim Volkov, a civilian who must plunder and fight his way through escaped mutant experiments, zombies, and military private contractors to reveal the truth about the Object 1611 disaster and find and save his sister, one of the scientists working within underground lower levels of the Object 1611 laboratory.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/cb781c463344ac1a7847285e629aa68b.avif?t=1716609862\" width=600 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Developer</h2>I am Vlad Bondarenco, a high schooler, and part-time game developer, and Containment Zone is my debut game release on steam. Containment Zone has been in the works for about 2 years now as I have been learning Unity Game Engine and C#, and I hope you enjoy! <br>If you like the game please share and support!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279490/extras/b672597a5312904602c8e187711cefbb.avif?t=1716609862\" width=400 height=532 /></span>",
